title: Cascading parameter values not displayed correctly in HTML viewer
description:
Description: Cascading parameter values are not displayed properly in the HTML viewer.

Steps to reproduce: 
1. Select the first parameter value in the cascading parameter group.

Observed Behavior (OB): The second parameter value in the same cascading parameter group is not displayed.

Expected Behavior (EB): The second parameter value should be displayed in the cascading parameter group in the HTML viewer.

Steps to Reproduce (SR):
1. Select the first parameter value and observe that the second parameter value in the same cascading parameter group is not displayed in the HTML viewer.
